e for section with handles inside</li>\n<li>Deprecated: Restore <code>get_page</code> method as hard deprecated (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/4870\" rel=\"nofollow\">#4870</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.1.1 &#8211; 2018-07-03</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Compatibility Gutenberg classic editor</li>\n<li>Fix: Compatibility for PHP &lt; 5.6</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.1.0 &#8211; 2018-07-03</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Introducing Elementor Context Menu</li>\n<li>New: Copy/Paste elements (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/4151\" rel=\"nofollow\">#4151</a>)</li>\n<li>New: Copy/Paste element style (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/1479\" rel=\"nofollow\">#1479</a>)</li>\n<li>New: Copy/Paste between pages</li>\n<li>New: Reset element style</li>\n<li>New: Added <code>copy_all_content</code> option</li>\n<li>New: Change mobile &amp; tablet breakpoints (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/78\" rel=\"nofollow\">#78</a>)</li>\n<li>New: Introducing Elementor WP-CLI integration (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/2161\" rel=\"nofollow\">#2161</a>)</li>\n<li>New: Added collapsable panel categories (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/3805\" rel=\"nofollow\">#3805</a>)</li>\n<li>New: Added Self hosted videos with HTML5 for Video widget (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/3313\" rel=\"nofollow\">#3313</a>)</li>\n<li>New: Added Dailymotion provider for Video widget (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/2285\" rel=\"nofollow\">#2285</a>)</li>\n<li>New: Added start/end controls for Video widget (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/3565\" rel=\"nofollow\">#3565</a>)</li>\n<li>New: Added new icons to Social Icons widget: Android &amp; Thumbtack (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/4235\" rel=\"nofollow\">#4235</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/4486\" rel=\"nofollow\">#4486</a>)</l