";}s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"4.8\";s:6:\"tested\";s:3:\"5.2\";s:10:\"stable_tag\";s:5:\"2.1.4\";s:8:\"sections\";O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:11:\"description\";s:166:\"<p>Premmerce Search makes the WooCommerce product search more flexible and efficient and gives the additional search results due to the spell correction.</p>\n\n<p></p>\";s:3:\"faq\";s:1053:\"<h4>Documentation</h4>\n\n<p>Full documentation is available here: <a href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-product-search/\">Premmerce Product Search for WooCommerce</a></p>\n\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n\n<p>Go to Plugins -> Add New section from your admin account and search for Premmerce Product Search for WooCommerce.</p>\n\n<p>You can also install this plugin manually:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Download the plugin’s ZIP archive and unzip it.</li>\n<li>Copy the unzipped premmerce-search folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the ‘Plugins’ menu in WordPress</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Does the plugin has shortcode for search form?</h4>\n\n<p>Yes, the plugin provides [premmerce_search] shortcode, that output\'s woocommerce search form with the live search.</p>\n\n<h4>Can I add the live search to custom search form?</h4>\n\n<p>Yes, you can enter the CSS selector of you search field on the plugin\'s settings page.\nFor example if you are using Ocean WP theme, you can add #s selector to make live search work as well.</p>\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:2786:\"<h4>1.0</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Oct 19, 2017</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>1.0.1</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Nov 20, 2017</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Added WordPress 4.9 support</li>\n<li>Added WooCommerce 3.2.4 support</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>1.1</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Dec 06, 2017</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Added price to autocomplete results</li>\n<li>Added Premmerce icon to menu</li>\n<li>Added Premmerce version check</li>\n<li>Added WordPress 4.9.1 support</li>\n<li>Added WooCommerce 3.2.5 support</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>1.1.1</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Jan 24, 2018</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed the dependency check on multisite</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>1.1.2</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Feb 02, 2018</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Added WooCommerce 3.3.0 support</li>\n<li>Updated translations</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>2.0</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Jun 15, 2018</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Updated SDK version</li>\n<li>Updated Freemius version</li>\n<li>Fixed autocomplete bug in storefront</li>\n<li>Fixed security issues</li>\n<li>Added WooCommerce 3.4 support</li>\n<li>Added search settings to premium version</li>\n<li>Added additional search fields to premium version</li>\n<li>Added \"View all results link\" to premium version</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>2.0.1</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Jun 15, 2018</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed custom database database prefix</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>2.0.2</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Jun 19, 2018</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Updated sku search query</li>\n<li>Fixed filter compatibility issues</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>2.0.3</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Jun 22, 2018</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed broken ACF query</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>2.0.4</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Jul 31, 2018</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed WPML permalinks</li>\n<li>Fixed autocomplete with cyrillic strings</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>2.0.5</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Aug 2, 2018</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed upgrade page</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>2.0.6</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Aug 14, 2018</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed invisible products in search results</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>2.0.7</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Nov 14, 2018</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Updated freemius version to 2.1.3</li>\n<li>Added WooCommerce 3.5 support</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>2.1</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Jan 16, 2019</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Added [premmerce_search] shortcode</li>\n<li>Added Force product search option</li>\n<li>Added Search field selector option</li>\n<li>Added spinner while live search processing</li>\n<li>Added OceanWp integration</li>\n<li>Updated freemius to 2.2.3</li>\n<li>Fixed uninstall hook</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>2.1.1</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Mar 1, 2019</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Security fix</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>2.1.2</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Apr 24, 2019</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Updated WooCommerce compatibility version to 3.6</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>2.1.3</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Jun 19, 2019</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Updated Premmerce SDK to 2.1</li>\n<li>Updated freemius to 2.3.0</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>2.1.4</h4>\n\n<p>Release Date: Sep 26, 2019</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Updated WooCommerce compatibility version to 3.7</li>\n</ul>\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:0:\"\";}s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";b:0;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"2.1.4\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:387:\"https://api.freemius.com/v1/installs/3614455/updates/11602.zip?is_premium=false&authorization=FSLA+3614455%3A9dfi8kGGckUYkwRyJhmKDWTo4Cl4F9b71_jdQB3i8AUFKbw1bP-Ks4Zx2AWNLYe2lLLICLO8mAkcYUnItCYm4jYJSpZNMV5VUzIawc4r77DNrjG2lalV4fN7Wf8yj6DLVGDgZqznupjzJqWqLEn6y14lolvpSPhNpjyhM8my3w7JxYcS64jbUfB9vhgC8cim9HJhlET2obEcYkKumyuNn1BEWxIFJ-2Kxmm6AenAf0mAGASXhDtuL6flhRvPdu4oM4Ipfvh9K1R3izgDUXGcew\";}}s:7:\"created\";i:1576690637;s:9:\"timestamp\";i:1576694237;}s:68:\"get:/v1/users/2504576/plugins/1520/payments.json?include_addons=true\";O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:6:\"result\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"payments\";a:0:{}}s:7:\"created\";i:1576690637;s:9:\"timestamp\";i:1576777037;}s:56:\"get:/v1/users/2504576.json?plugin_id=2086&fields=is_beta\";O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:6:\"result\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:2:\"id\";s:7:\"2504576\";s:7:\"is_beta\";b:0;}s:7:\"created\";i:1576771778;s:9:\"timestamp\";i:1576858178;}s:45:\"get:/v1/users/2504576/plugins/2086/plans.json\";O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:6:\"result\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:5:\"plans\";a:3:{i:0;O:14:\"FS_Plugin_Plan\":21:{s:9:\"plugin_id\";s:4:\"2086\";s:4:\"name\";s:4:\"free\";s:5:\"title\";s:7:\"Starter\";s:11:\"description\";s:13:\"Basic Options\";s:17:\"is_free_localhost\";b:1;s:17:\"is_block_features\";b:1;s:12:\"license_type\";i:0;s:16:\"is_https_support\";b:0;s:12:\"trial_period\";N;s:23:\"is_require_subscription\";b:0;s:10:\"support_kb\";N;s:13:\"support_forum\";s:32:\"https://ivorysearch.com/support/\";s:13:\"sup